'''Blademaster''' was the title given to the [[Lightsaber combat/Legends|lightsaber combat]] instructor at the [[Sith Academy (Korriban)|Sith Academy]] of [[Korriban/Legends|Korriban]]. [[Kas'im]] held the position at the end of the [[New Sith Wars]]. The [[Military rank/Legends|rank]] of the [[Sith/Legends|Sith's]] Blademaster was on par with the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi's]] [[Battlemaster/Legends|Battlemaster]]. They supposedly knew all lightsaber forms to a degree of excellence that they could instruct pupils in the art. The lightsaber class began in the morning and at the end of the practice session, apprentices were able to challenge each other under the Blademaster's supervision. If they weren't vigilant, deaths could occur.

